<title>USA: IPO PRICING - Peritus prices above range.</title>
<headline>IPO PRICING - Peritus prices above range.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-07-02</dateline>
<text>
<p>Company Name	     Peritus Software Inc</p>
<p>   Priced At					 $16</p>
<p>   Estimated Pricing Range	     $12 - $14</p>
<p>   Number of Shares			3,500,000</p>
<p>   Lead Underwriter	Montgomery Securities</p>
<p>NOTE: Terms were modified for the planned initial public offering in Peritus Software Inc. The estimated price range was raised to $12 to $14 from $10 to $12 initially and the proposed number of shares on offer were 3.5 million shares, up from 2.9 million shares previously.</p>
</text>
